OL,3,CNHS issues national alert over
OL,4,Cshortage of certain blood types
OL,6,FThe NHS has made an urgent appeal for
OL,7,Fpeople to give blood, as national
OL,8,Fstocks of O negative and O positive
OL,9,Fhave fallen to unprecedented low
OL,10,Flevels.
OL,12,FIncreased demand from hospitals and
OL,13,Fhigh levels of unfilled appointments
OL,14,Fat donor centres have created "a
OL,15,Fperfect storm", NHS Blood and
OL,16,FTransplant (NHSBT) said.
OL,18,FIt is just the second time such an
OL,19,Falert has been issued, with the only
OL,20,Fother incident happening in October
OL,21,F2022.
