OL,3,CNHS issues national alert over
OL,4,Cshortage of certain blood types
OL,6,FNHSBT wrote to hospitals on Thursday
OL,7,Fto issue an "amber alert", asking them
OL,8,Fto restrict the use of O type blood to
OL,9,Fessential cases and use substitutions
OL,10,Fwhere possible.
OL,12,FThe alert is set off when blood levels
OL,13,Ffall below two days' worth of stock.
OL,15,FLevels of O negative, are currently at
OL,16,F1.6 days, while overall national
OL,17,Fstocks of all blood types is 4.3 days.
