OL,3,CNHS issues national alert over
OL,4,Cshortage of certain blood types
OL,6,FO negative, which makes up around 16%
OL,7,Fof hospital orders, can be used in
OL,8,Femergencies or when a patient's blood
OL,9,Ftype is unknown.
OL,11,FNHSBT chief executive Dr Jo Farrar
OL,12,Fsaid: "Last month we saw an incredible
OL,13,Fresponse from donors who answered our
OL,14,Fcall and filled up our centres,
OL,15,Fhelping us meet the increased demands
OL,16,Ffor blood throughout June.
OL,18,F"However, seven weeks on, the need for
OL,19,FO negative blood in particular remains
OL,20,Fcritical."
