OL,3,CNHS issues national alert over
OL,4,Cshortage of certain blood types
OL,6,FNHSBT said the ongoing cyber incident
OL,7,Fwhich affected several London
OL,8,Fhospitals last month had also impacted
OL,9,FO negative stocks, with a 94% increase
OL,10,Fin demand compared with the same
OL,11,Fperiod last year.
OL,13,FSeveral hospitals, including King's
OL,14,FCollege Hospital, Guy's and St
OL,15,FThomas', declared a critical incident
OL,16,Fand cancelled operations after the
OL,17,Fattack on the pathology firm Synnovis.
