OL,3,CNHS issues national alert over
OL,4,Cshortage of certain blood types
OL,6,FThere are just under 800,000 regular
OL,7,Fblood donors nationally, but blood has
OL,8,Fa shelf life of only 35 days, NHSBT's
OL,9,Fchief medical officer Dr Gail Miflin
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FWomen can donate once every four
OL,13,Fmonths, while men can donate once
OL,14,Fevery three months.
OL,16,FTo book an appointment to give blood,
OL,17,Fcall 0300 123 23 23 or visit
OL,18,Fwww.blood.co.uk.
